msgstr "# triton.language.advance"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：将`tl.make_block_ptr`的offset增加一个偏移量\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Add an offset to the offset of `tl.make_block_ptr`  \n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.advance(\n"
" base: triton.PointerType,\n"
" offsets: tuple(int | constexpr),\n"
" _semantic=None\n"
")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `base`        | `triton.PointerType`          |需要被更新的指针，`tl.make_block_ptr`的结果                                |\n"
"| `offsets`     | `tuple(int \\| constexpr)`    | 张量各维度的基址偏移量列表，`len(offsets)`需要与`len(base.offsets)`相等 |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用|\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type                | Description                                                                 |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `base`        | `triton.PointerType`          | The pointer to be updated, result of `tl.make_block_ptr`                     |\n"
"| `offsets`     | `tuple(int \\| constexpr)`    | List of base offsets for each dimension of the tensor; `len(offsets)` must equal `len(base.offsets)` |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now                     |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:14
msgid "返回值：`pointer_type<blocked<shape, element_type>>`： 指向tensor的指针"
msgstr "Return value: `pointer_type<blocked<shape, element_type>>`: pointer to the tensor"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:20
msgid ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √    | √     | √     | √     | √      | √      | √      | √     | √    | √    | √    | √    | ×    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | ×    |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √    | √     | √     | √     | √      | √      | √      | √     | √    | √    | √    | √    | ×    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | ×    |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:22
msgid "结论：Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）。"
msgstr "Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation)."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:24
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:26
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:28
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both support 1 to 5 dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:30
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:32
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "> Relative community capability deficiency and inability to achieve"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:34
msgid ""
"- Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint8、uint16、uint32、uint64、fp64的支持能力（硬件限制）。\n"
"- Ascend只允许通过调整`order`参数的顺序来表达转置语义，不能通过调整`stride`参数的顺序实现转置语义。\n"
"- 当前`tl.make_tensor_ptr`，如果与较复杂的循环和分支语句搭配使用，可能会出现编译问题\n"
msgstr ""
"- Ascend lacks support for uint8, uint16, uint32, uint64, and fp64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation).\n"
"- Ascend only allows expressing transpose semantics by adjusting the order of the `order` parameter, not by adjusting the order of the `stride` parameter.\n"
"- Currently, `tl.make_tensor_ptr` may cause compilation issues when used with complex loops and branch statements.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:38
msgid "参考以下示例："
msgstr "Refer to the following example:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/tl.advance.md:40
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def fn_npu_3d(output_ptr, x_ptr, y_ptr, z_ptr, output_ptr1, XB: tl.constexpr, YB: tl.constexpr, ZB: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    block_ptr_in = tl.make_block_ptr(\n"
"        base=x_ptr,\n"
"        shape=(XB, YB, ZB),\n"
"        strides=(YB * ZB, ZB, 1),\n"
"        offsets=(3, 1, 2),\n"
"        block_shape=(XB, YB, ZB),\n"
"        order=(2, 1, 0),\n"
"    )\n"
"    bbptr = tl.advance(block_ptr_in, (-3, -1, -2))\n"
"    # XB,YB,1\n"
"    X = tl.load(bbptr)\n"
"\n"
"    block_ptr_out = tl.make_block_ptr(\n"
"        base=output_ptr,\n"
"        shape=(XB, YB, ZB),\n"
"        strides=(YB * ZB, ZB, 1),\n"
"        offsets=(0, 0, 0),\n"
"        block_shape=(XB, YB, ZB),\n"
"        order=(2, 1, 0),\n"
"    )\n"
"    tl.store(block_ptr_out, X)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

